## 概述

Bybit V5 是统一 API，覆盖 Spot/Derivatives/Options。Linear Perpetual = USDT 保证金永续合约。

| 项目 | 值 |
|------|-----|
| REST Mainnet | `https://api.bybit.com` |
| REST Testnet | `https://api-testnet.bybit.com` |
| WS Public Linear | `wss://stream.bybit.com/v5/public/linear` |
| WS Private | `wss://stream.bybit.com/v5/private` |
| WS Trade | `wss://stream.bybit.com/v5/trade` |
| Testnet WS | `stream-testnet.bybit.com` |
| 认证方式 | HMAC-SHA256 |
| 账户类型 | Unified Trading Account |
| Python SDK | `pip install pybit` |

